Use the standard library
This is how to get_closest_vowel of word:
   Remember that vowels is "aeiouAEIOU"
   Remember that n is word's length
   Remember that i is diff of n and 1
   Do this n times:
      Remember that c is item i in word
      When c is in vowels, then:
         The answer is c
      End when
      Decrease i
   End do
   The answer is ""
